direction: right

User: Human Developer
Agent: Autonomous AI (Antigravity)
Rules: Governance Constraints (.agents/rules/)
Merge: Conflict Resolution Workflow
Scaffold: App Construction (src/)
Verify: Eval Suite (pytest)

User -> Agent: "Initialize new project using Base Environment"

Agent -> Rules: 1. Read strict 12-factor constraints
Agent -> Merge: 2. Execute safe merge protocol
Merge -> Scaffold: 3. Mechanically build Application Plane
Scaffold -> Verify: 4. Run deterministic & probabilistic evals
Verify -> User: 5. Handover fully operational environment

# Styling for Sketch Mode
classes: {
  actor: {
    style: {
      fill: "#238636"
      font-color: white
      border-radius: 10
    }
  }
  system: {
    style: {
      fill: "#1f6feb"
      font-color: white
    }
  }
}

User.class: actor
Agent.class: actor
Rules.class: system
Merge.class: system
Scaffold.class: system
Verify.class: system
